Today, I rose to speak in unwavering support of our nation’s federal employees, including the thousands in Texas’ 18th Congressional District. 

America needs its federal workforce, and we will continue to stand firm in protecting their rights, jobs, and dedication to public service.

@Labor_Caucus

Today, along with Ranking Member on Homeland Security, Congressman Bennie Thompson, and my other colleagues, we sent a letter to the Office of Management and Budget (OMB) demanding that the administration adhere to all Federal data protection laws. 

This recent overreach by Elon Musk and (DOGE) is potential violation of Federal law and raises serious national security concerns that must be addressed immediately.

